{"type": "article", "id": 13104, "title": "珍藏夏日记忆——阳伞变包袋", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-06T06:49:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155848CtOpPRLo7shxbyFU.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t八月是夏天，也是秋天，一进八月就觉得夏天好像快要过完了似的。你有没有想过怎样保存夏天的记忆呀？Marcella De Faveri 和 Marta Foschi 两位设计师这样做的：他们回收了所在的海滨城市的废弃的阳伞，经过简单的加工后，做成了一个个的书包，为吹了一个夏天海风的阳伞带来了新的活力，而书包的图案也因为阳伞图案的多样而充满各种奇妙的可能性。这是<a href=\"http://www.riminiriminibags.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140727dN3qxiBY74Te6vgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140727EtVR20DbTdWLYeBP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67114914\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140728R9JS1ax6WowVjh84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140728sXxKW4ALgePNMtaR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140729Zd9itKLevNXxJqs8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49388753\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407295mkzjTPRSUYNMos8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}